We're at the third
annual Goop Summit,

22:39.101 --> 22:41.059
Goop being
the wellness brand

22:41.142 --> 22:43.558
that was started
by Gwyneth Paltrow.

22:43.642 --> 22:45.184
It was once fringe,

22:45.267 --> 22:47.725
but as you can see,
from the steady stream

22:47.809 --> 22:49.684
of well-turned out,
